        <div class="bento-content">
          <div class="fcard-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Zero-Config Discovery Engine</h3>
          <p>Scans your file system and autonomously locates <code>.pi</code> workspaces, <code>.codex</code> logs, and OpenCode databases without manual configuration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-visual">
          <div class="infinite-scroll-y" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="scroll-content">
              <div class="log-line"><span class="ti">scan</span> ~/.pi/agent/sessions/</div>
              <div class="log-line"><span class="ti">scan</span> ~/.codex/sessions/</div>
              <div class="log-line"><span class="ti">connect</span> ~/.opencode/opencode.db</div>
              <div class="log-line dim">mapped 1,248 events</div>
              <div class="log-line"><span class="ti">scan</span> ~/.pi/agent/sessions/</div>
              <div class="log-line"><span class="ti">scan</span> ~/.codex/sessions/</div>
              <div class="log-line"><span class="ti">connect</span> ~/.opencode/opencode.db</div>
              <div class="log-line dim">mapped 1,248 events</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item liquid-glass">
        <div class="bento-content">
          <div class="fcard-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Dynamic Pricing</h3>
          <p>Synchronizes with LiteLLM's pricing repository with offline caching for isolated environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-visual">
          <div class="pulse-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="text">Syncing LiteLLM</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-item liquid-glass">
        <div class="bento-content">
          <div class="fcard-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"/>
            </svg>
